{"tid":1629323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"就到萬聖節，大家不宜裝修，應改為幫店舖裝飾","createTime":"2019-10-06T08:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:15:37.000Z","uid":3508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a493843167166422c1b150847a29946439d369","tid":1629323,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"等待美國人權法通過，再進行裝修<br />\n依家用標語，油彩，貼圖進行裝飾，可以增添節日氣氛而不失行動之力，也能繼續為各被捕手足出返啖氣<br />\n本人並非反對裝修，而係人權法比一時發洩重要，我地都唔係怕左蒙面法，正如狗呢幾日都收兵咁，就係等人大肆破滅營造負面形象<br />\n為左更長遠既利益，希望大家三思，等真春袋人權法過左先，真係忍唔到就去幫黨鐵裝修，其他裝飾住先"},{"pid":"edd71f695e7d25d7d8c7d762577c3aa2999ec1d0","tid":1629323,"uid":68686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:17:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔想害死裝修師嘅<br />\n馬上入黎推到佢地睇到</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">裝修要提防 做好安全措施<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625622</a></span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c7686920bf37c364cc29f8c71392c28393436bb5","tid":1629323,"uid":215296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:27:41.000Z","msg":"我知大家好心急 呢關其實要考驗大家耐性 來日方長"},{"pid":"f9ebb8fe313754255986c8db0bfaa5a7911f866d","tid":1629323,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3YDZk79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3YDZk79.png&h=212af3d5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}